org.sakaiproject.api.app.messageforums

Interface AreaManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AreaManagerImpl

    public interface AreaManager
    The Area id the high level object of the object model. Typicaly a site can contain up to 2 Areas - a Discussion Area and a Private Message Area
    Author:
    rshastri
